{"tid":1313784,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【毋忘初衷】唔好令「沒有暴徒，只有暴政」變成鳩噏！","createTime":"2019-07-14T02:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T02:43:25.000Z","uid":271139,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1fd511b6669ff1c4e22a336166723261e9fb6750","tid":1313784,"uid":271139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:02:17.000Z","msg":"各位同路人，明白大家對呢個仆街政府好失望、好憤怒！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係希望大家唔好忘記，成個抗爭裡面，我地嗌得最響亮嘅其中一個口號係：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">「沒有暴徒，只有暴政！」</span></span></span></strong><br />\n對於「暴徒」，大家有唔同定義，但<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地要有底線&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n唔可以主動傷害他人身體！</span></span></strong>（無論佢係差佬、自己人定普通市民）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拜託大家互相提醒，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好畀林鄭、盧偉聰嗰班廢柴有藉口話我地係暴徒！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"faf7f37de320893fbd43fff4205ff2f107edf03e","tid":1313784,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:06:22.000Z","msg":"全部同我入黎！教你下一步點做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1313709\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1313709</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c06988b43cd075a445ea62da6aaed3c2d758c9a1","tid":1313784,"uid":269119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fd511b6669ff1c4e22a336166723261e9fb6750","tid":1313784,"uid":271139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:02:17.000Z","msg":"各位同路人，明白大家對呢個仆街政府好失望、好憤怒！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係希望大家唔好忘記，成個抗爭裡面，我地嗌得最響亮嘅其中一個口號係：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">「沒有暴徒，只有暴政！」</span></span></span></strong><br />\n對於「暴徒」，大家有唔同定義，但<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地要有底線&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n唔可以主動傷害他人身體！</span></span></strong>（無論佢係差佬、自己人定普通市民）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拜託大家互相提醒，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好畀林鄭、盧偉聰嗰班廢柴有藉口話我地係暴徒！</span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:20:48.000Z","msg":"噉如果你想人還擊，會有訊號表示嗎？"},{"pid":"f5d4407e99ea5964b491fb79aa80239b42db68b1","tid":1313784,"uid":266503,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:43:01.000Z","msg":"槍響之前：金恩博士與三個邪惡的最後鬥爭<br />\n人們當然知道馬丁路德金恩博士為黑人民權運動奮鬥，知道他著名的演說「我有一個夢」，或者知道他在整整五十年前的1968年被槍殺。<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@soundfury/%E6%A7%8D%E9%9F%BF%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D-%E9%87%91%E6%81%A9%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E8%88%87%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E9%82%AA%E6%83%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E9%AC%A5%E7%88%AD-c3dd35a3dcf4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40soundfury%2F%25E6%25A7%258D%25E9%259F%25BF%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%2589%258D-%25E9%2587%2591%25E6%2581%25A9%25E5%258D%259A%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%2580%258B%25E9%2582%25AA%25E6%2583%25A1%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%25AC%25A5%25E7%2588%25AD-c3dd35a3dcf4&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtUL8yZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=1e85a830\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@soundfury/%E6%A7%8D%E9%9F%BF%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D-%E9%87%91%E6%81%A9%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB%E8%88%87%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E9%82%AA%E6%83%A1%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E9%AC%A5%E7%88%AD-c3dd35a3dcf4</a><br />\n泛民，要學馬丁路德金。<br />\n我不反對不支持勇武，但理解。請在勇武前冷靜想清楚後果(自己和旁人）.不受傷，不流血。<br />\n「我有一個夢」背後有「選票與子彈」支持同保護<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/選票還是子彈\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E9%81%B8%E7%A5%A8%E9%82%84%E6%98%AF%E5%AD%90%E5%BD%88&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtUL8yZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=7a3f9102\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/選票還是子彈</a>"},{"pid":"f520062246472e5876eaf37e7eff44c34b613de4","tid":1313784,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:43:25.000Z","msg":"push"}]}